author: stsp
msg: Revert r1161219, which made 'svn merge' apply incoming edits to locally
moved-away files. We're going to let 'svn merge' flag a tree conflict
and handle resolution within 'svn resolve' instead.
(merge_file_changed): Flag an "incoming edit vs. local moved-away" tree
conflict instead of merging into the file at its moved-here location.
